Target System                  — Asset under analysis
│
├─ Network Discovery           — Is it reachable?
│   ├─ ping                    — Host availability (ICMP)
│   ├─ fping                   — Fast host discovery
│   └─ traceroute              — Network path mapping
│
├─ Name & Asset Discovery      — What is it called?
│   ├─ DNS                     — Name resolution
│   ├─ dig / nslookup          — DNS query tools
│   ├─ amass                   — Asset & subdomain discovery
│   └─ subfinder               — Passive subdomain enumeration
│
├─ Port & Service Mapping      — What is exposed?
│   ├─ nmap                    — Port & service discovery
│   ├─ masscan                 — Large‑scale port scanning
│   └─ rustscan                — Fast port discovery
│
├─ Web Surface Enumeration     — What endpoints exist?
│   ├─ httpx                   — HTTP service probing
│   ├─ hakrawler               — URL crawling
│   ├─ gau                     — Known URL collection
│   └─ waybackurls             — Historical endpoints
│
├─ Parameter & Input Discovery — Where is user input?
│   ├─ arjun                   — Parameter discovery
│   ├─ paramspider             — Parameter mining
│   └─ qsreplace               — Query manipulation
│
├─ Vulnerability Detection     — What is weak?
│   ├─ nuclei                  — Template‑based scanning
│   ├─ nikto                   — Web server checks
│   ├─ testssl.sh              — TLS misconfiguration
│   └─ wpscan                  — CMS‑specific scanning
│
├─ Exploitation Frameworks     — Can weakness be used?
│   ├─ metasploit              — Exploit framework
│   ├─ msfconsole              — Exploit orchestration
│   └─ exploitdb               — Public exploit reference
│
├─ Post‑Discovery Analysis     — What data leaks?
│   ├─ gf                      — Pattern‑based filtering
│   ├─ anew                    — Deduplication
│   └─ unfurl                  — URL component extraction
│
├─ Content & Secret Discovery  — What is exposed accidentally?
│   ├─ ffuf                    — Content fuzzing
│   ├─ dirsearch               — Directory discovery
│   ├─ trufflehog              — Secret detection
│   └─ git‑dumper               — Repo leakage detection
│
├─ Traffic & Behavior Analysis — How does it behave?
│   ├─ burpsuite               — HTTP inspection
│   ├─ mitmproxy               — Traffic interception
│   └─ wireshark               — Packet analysis
│
└─ Reporting & Automation      — Scale & repeat
    ├─ bash / python           — Automation glue
    ├─ cron / CI               — Scheduled scanning
    └─ dashboards              — Findings visibility

